snippet.title: Mail Time - Official Gameplay Trailer | Wholesome Snack: The Game Awards Edition
snippet.description:
In Mail Time, your quest to deliver a letter to Greg turns into an adventure where you, as a newly trained Mail Scout, must deliver parcels across the colorful Grumblewood Grove. A special demo is now available on Steam.
